Class Controller.LocationTagContent

java.lang.Object
sample.Controller.LocationTagContent
Enclosing class:
Controller
public static class Controller.LocationTagContent
extends java.lang.Object

Location Tag Content

This class allows to format and prepare the Locations of a Request (Pickup or Delivery) into textual raw data to be displayed on the Timeline listview
